---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Exterior Painting Services - CallBrownsPainting.com"
  description="Professional exterior painting services in Gulf Shores, Orange Beach, Foley, Daphne, Fairhope, Spanish Fort, Brewton, Atmore and all South Alabama areas. Salt air resistant paint, deck staining, coastal home painting."
  keywords="exterior painting Gulf Shores AL, beach house painting Orange Beach AL, deck staining Foley AL, salt air paint damage Orange Beach, coastal home painting contractors, exterior repainting Gulf Shores AL"
>
  <main>
    <section class="service-hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Professional Exterior Painting Services</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          Protect and beautify your property with expert exterior painting services throughout South Alabama. 
          From Gulf Shores to Brewton, we specialize in coastal and inland weather-resistant solutions.
        </p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Free Estimate</a>
          <a href="#services" class="btn btn-secondary">View Services</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="services-detailed">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Exterior Painting Services We Offer</h2>
        
        <div class="service-grid">
          <article class="service-item">
            <h3>House Siding & Trim</h3>
            <p>
              Complete exterior house painting with weather-resistant paints designed for Alabama's climate. 
              We prepare surfaces properly to ensure long-lasting results.
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Vinyl siding painting</li>
              <li>Wood siding restoration</li>
              <li>Aluminum siding repainting</li>
              <li>Trim and fascia painting</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="service-item">
            <h3>Deck & Porch Painting</h3>
            <p>
              Professional deck staining and porch painting services. We use premium stains and paints 
              that resist moisture, UV damage, and foot traffic.
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Deck staining and sealing</li>
              <li>Porch floor painting</li>
              <li>Railings and balusters</li>
              <li>Pressure washing preparation</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="service-item">
            <h3>Coastal Home Protection</h3>
            <p>
              Specialized painting for coastal properties in Gulf Shores, Orange Beach, and Foley. 
              Salt air resistant paints and techniques for maximum protection.
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Salt air resistant paint systems</li>
              <li>Beach house exterior painting</li>
              <li>Vacation rental repainting</li>
              <li>Coastal weather protection</li>
            </ul>
          </article>

          <article class="service-item">
            <h3>Fence & Gate Painting</h3>
            <p>
              Extend the life of your fences and gates with professional painting services. 
              We use durable paints that resist weather and wear.
            </p>
            <ul>
              <li>Wood fence painting</li>
              <li>Metal gate painting</li>
              <li>Chain link fence painting</li>
              <li>Privacy fence staining</li>
            </ul>
          </article>
        </div>

        <section class="problem-solutions">
          <h2>Common Exterior Painting Problems We Solve</h2>
          
          <div class="problem-grid">
            <div class="problem-item">
              <h3>Salt Air Paint Damage</h3>
              <p>
                Coastal properties in Orange Beach and Gulf Shores face unique challenges from salt air. 
                We use specialized paints and preparation techniques to prevent corrosion and fading.
              </p>
              <p><strong>Areas:</strong> Gulf Shores, Orange Beach, Foley, Fairhope, Spanish Fort</p>
            </div>

            <div class="problem-item">
              <h3>Faded Exterior Paint</h3>
              <p>
                Alabama's intense sun can cause paint to fade quickly. We use UV-resistant paints 
                and proper application techniques for lasting color and protection.
              </p>
              <p><strong>Areas:</strong> All South Alabama communities</p>
            </div>

            <div class="problem-item">
              <h3>Moisture & Mildew Issues</h3>
              <p>
                High humidity can cause paint to peel and mildew to form. We use moisture-resistant 
                paints and proper ventilation techniques to prevent these problems.
              </p>
              <p><strong>Areas:</strong> Eastern Shore (Daphne, Fairhope), Coastal areas</p>
            </div>

            <div class="problem-item">
              <h3>Aluminum Siding Repainting</h3>
              <p>
                Aluminum siding requires special preparation and paint systems. We clean, prime, 
                and paint with products designed specifically for metal surfaces.
              </p>
              <p><strong>Areas:</strong> Stapleton, Robertsdale, Summerdale, Bay Minette</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="coastal-specialties">
          <h2>Coastal Painting Specialties</h2>
          <p>
            Our coastal painting expertise covers the unique challenges of beachfront and near-coast properties:
          </p>
          
          <div class="specialty-grid">
            <div class="specialty-item">
              <h3>Beach House Painting</h3>
              <p>
                Specialized painting for beach houses in Gulf Shores and Orange Beach. 
                We understand the unique challenges of coastal properties.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Salt air resistant paint systems</li>
                <li>Wind and sand damage protection</li>
                <li>Moisture barrier applications</li>
                <li>UV protection coatings</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="specialty-item">
              <h3>Vacation Rental Repainting</h3>
              <p>
                Fast, efficient repainting services for vacation rental properties. 
                We work around rental schedules to minimize disruption.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Quick turnaround times</li>
                <li>Durable, easy-maintenance finishes</li>
                <li>Guest-friendly scheduling</li>
                <li>Property management partnerships</li>
              </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="specialty-item">
              <h3>Deck & Dock Staining</h3>
              <p>
                Professional deck and dock staining for coastal properties. 
                We use marine-grade stains that resist salt water and weather.
              </p>
              <ul>
                <li>Marine-grade stain systems</li>
                <li>Salt water resistance</li>
                <li>Slip-resistant finishes</li>
                <li>Regular maintenance programs</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="service-areas">
          <h2>Exterior Painting Service Areas</h2>
          <p>
            We provide professional exterior painting services throughout South Alabama:
          </p>
          
          <div class="areas-grid">
            <div class="area-column">
              <h3>Coastal Baldwin County</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Gulf Shores - Beach house painting specialists</li>
                <li>Orange Beach - Salt air resistant painting</li>
                <li>Foley - Coastal home exterior painting</li>
                <li>Fairhope - Eastern Shore exterior painting</li>
                <li>Daphne - Professional house painting</li>
                <li>Spanish Fort - Exterior repainting services</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="area-column">
              <h3>Inland Baldwin County</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Bay Minette - Farm and barn painting</li>
                <li>Loxley - Residential exterior painting</li>
                <li>Robertsdale - Commercial exterior painting</li>
                <li>Summerdale - House painting services</li>
                <li>Stapleton - Aluminum siding repainting</li>
                <li>Perdido - Exterior painting contractors</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="area-column">
              <h3>Escambia & Conecuh Counties</h3>
              <ul>
                <li>Brewton - Professional exterior painting</li>
                <li>Atmore - Residential house painting</li>
                <li>Flomaton - Exterior repainting services</li>
                <li>Evergreen - Home exterior painting</li>
                <li>Monroeville - Professional house painting</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-section">
          <h2>Ready for Professional Exterior Painting?</h2>
          <p>
            Contact Barry "Boomer" Brown today for a free estimate on your exterior painting project. 
            We specialize in coastal and inland weather-resistant painting solutions.
          </p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Free Exterior Painting Estimate</a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

